---
title: Middle Eastern Pork & Zesty Garlic Yoghurt with Roast Veggie Israeli Couscous & Pistachios
description: We’re dressing up tender pork to impress anyone who sits at your table. You’ve got the works: from the roasted pumpkin and cauliflower sprinkled with pistachios to the zesty yoghurt, everything is so eye-catching. The Middle Eastern-spiced pork though will leave the lasting impression of a five-star taste experience.
